This program is currently under development.

New functionality is being added.

YOU MUST HAVE ARCGIS 10 and .NET FRAMEWORK 3.5 INSTALLED IN ORDER TO RUN THIS PROGRAM. THIS PROGRAM IS AN ESRI ADD-IN PROJECT AND CAN BE INSTALLED BY DOUBLE CLICKING THE ADDIN FILE.

The addin currently supports creation of Ordinary Voronoi Diagrams from input points, lines or polygon files.

As of 05/29/2013, the program supports creation of Multiplicatively Weighted Voronoi Diagrams from input points, lines or polygon files.



For questions or comments, contact Pinliang Dong at pdong@unt.edu.